Name:		glite-build-common-cpp
Version:	3.2.12.2
Release:	1
Summary:	gLite build macros

Group:		Development/Libraries/C and C++
License:	Apache 2.0
URL:		http://glite.cvs.cern.ch/cgi-bin/glite.cgi/org.glite.build.common-cpp/
